OOC: AOL sent my mail before I could finish.

In another time, The Infecticons selected to pursue the X-Predacons all work 
hastily at their respected consoles. Soon the massive pyramid like ship with 
Metalk attachements all along its base(if anyone watches Stargate Sg-1 its 
the ship that was in the last ep of season 4 but not nearly as big as it) 
rises from a hole in the Infecticon homeworld. Soon a portal opens in front 
of the Bamphomet leading back in time and to Prehistoric earth. And without a 
word spoken among its crew the ship speeds off into the portal...

--part1_85.b7557af.284b8809_boundary
